    <p>This app will allow you to create an audit project, add the cycles necessary and create tasks within those cycles. You can then assign staff to those tasks so you'll never have to worry about them not knowing what to work on.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="large-4 columns">
    <div class='block-images'>
      <%= image_tag('Auditors-auditors-everywhere.jpg') %>
