    <p>Being able to view how each audit is progressing and what workpapers are ready to be reviewed or are still open will allow you as a manager or partner to quickly glance at one screen and be able to guage the progress being made. You will also have the ability to drill down to individual tasks as necessary.</p>
  </div>

